---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="About — yourname" description="A bit about me.">
  <h1 class="page-title">About</h1>
  <div class="prose">
    <p>
      Hi! My name is Ic-Q. I usually go by my pseudonym: 7qffza5d. This is my blog/portfolio 
      website. I will be writing about anything that amuses me, but mainly I will write about 
      Computer Science and Linguistics. I will try to hold myself to at least one essay 
      per week, but no promises.
    </p>
    <p>
      I am a student at SCiUS program at UBU. I have been drawn to programming since I was a child.
      I am a stage 2 student of the Informatics Olympiad - for now at least, fingers crossed. Through
      the academic olympiad world, I was brought to linguistics. Even though linguistics is norminally
      the study of languages, which are nominally entirely human created, so you'd think it would be the
      furthest thing from CS. But I found that's not the case. I think they are both manifestations of
      human ideas, just in different forms. So I want to at least bridge this gap between the two worlds
      and offer ideas viewed through a new lens. If that sounds like something you would be interested in,
      feel free to stick around. 
    </p>
  </div>
  <ul class="social-links">
    <li>
      <a href="https://github.com/7qffza5d" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"><path d="M9 19c-4.3 1.4-4.3-2.5-6-3m12 5v-3.5c0-1 .1-1.4-.5-2 2.8-.3 5.5-1.4 5.5-6a4.6 4.6 0 0 0-1.3-3.2 4.2 4.2 0 0 0-.1-3.2s-1.1-.3-3.5 1.3a12.3 12.3 0 0 0-6.2 0C6.5 2.8 5.4 3.1 5.4 3.1a4.2 4.2 0 0 0-.1 3.2A4.6 4.6 0 0 0 4 9.5c0 4.6 2.7 5.7 5.5 6-.6.6-.6 1.2-.5 2V21"/></svg>
        <span>GitHub</span>
      </a>
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="https://instagram.com/kritkutawan" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="5"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4"/><circle cx="17.5" cy="6.5" r="0.9" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/></svg>
        <span>Instagram</span>
      </a>
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="https://facebook.com/kvs.n.ku.ta.wan" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"><path d="M9 21v-8H6v-3h3V8.5C9 5.9 10.6 4 13.2 4H16v3.2h-2c-1 0-1.3.5-1.3 1.4V10h3.3l-.5 3H12.7v8"/></svg>
        <span>Facebook</span>
      </a>
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="https://www.chess.com/member/7qffza5d" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"><path d="M12 3c-1.4 0-2.5 1-2.5 2.3 0 .8.4 1.4 1 1.9-1.3.5-2 1.7-2 3.3h7c0-1.6-.7-2.8-2-3.3.6-.5 1-1.1 1-1.9C14.5 4 13.4 3 12 3Z"/><path d="M8.5 10.5h7l1 8h-9l1-8Z"/><path d="M6.5 20.5h11"/></svg>
